            <bioghist>
                <p>Louis Cephas Madeira Sr. (1819-1896) was a fire insurance agent. He married
                    Adeline Laura Powell in 1850. They had six children, Kate P., Louis C., Henry,
                    Adeline, Percy and Edith. </p>
            </bioghist>

            <scopecontent>
                <p>This is a collection of eight scrapbooks kept by Louis C. Madeira. Subjects of
                    the scrapbooks include famous Philadelphians, wit and humor, famous portraits,
                    and miscellaneous Americana. The scrapbooks contain newspaper and magazine
                    clippings.</p>
            </scopecontent>


